# Grab a `.gitignore` file template.
#
# Arguments:
#   $1 (str): Name of `.gitignore` template.
#
# STDOUT:
#   The `.gitignore` file contents if a template is found.
#   Undefined error if no template exists by the given name.
#
# Examples:
#   gi python
#   gi ruby > .gitignore
#
curl -L -s https://www.gitignore.io/api/$@ ;

